{
  "stem": "734.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, eventually, so, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] so what actually happened is that most of the Jewish-owned businesses simply were confiscated or went down, were taken over by other people, non-Jewish people, were sold on a block, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the ones that were doing well, well, then they were-- like I said, what-- the same thing would happened to the studio.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Well--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The armbands were issued-- the armband-- the decree about the armbands was issued something like two weeks after-- a week, 10 days after they came in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The first thing was to mark us, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the first thing, yes, that they did, to close up educational institutions and mark us, the armbands, yes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not every city had the same, had the same armbands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other cities, they had the Star of David, a yellow Star of David in, in, in the, in the, the lapel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know why they didn't have it all the same all over the place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they had different ways of marking us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had an armband.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a white armband with a blue Star of David.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The armband, it must have been like, I would say, four inches wide. three and a half to four inches wide.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Star of David was just as wide as the armband in the center.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you had to have it on your outer garment at all the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if you were caught without the star, without the armband and you were identified as, as a Jew, they shot you on the, on the spot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So-- and of course, re-- restrictions had no limit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were absolutely hundreds and hundreds of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was almost impossible to memorize.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
